## [Date: 2024-12-19] - Initial Creation

### Created
- Skill created via creating-skills workflow
- RED failure documented: Threat modeling Phase 3 lacks standardized CVSS scoring with business context integration
- Category: security (skill-library)
- Type: Process/Pattern (CVSS scoring methodology)
- Target: Standalone open-source threat modeling tool
- Key features:
  - CVSS version selection (3.1 recommended, 4.0 optional)
  - Base metric assessment for theoretical threats
  - Temporal/Threat metrics with conservative defaults
  - Environmental metrics auto-derived from Phase 0 business context
  - Structured JSON output for threat-model.json

